---
name: update_dashboard
description: Update the Dashboard.md with current vault statistics and status
model: recommended
---

You are responsible for keeping the Dashboard.md up to date.

## Steps
1. Count items in each folder:
   - /Needs_Action - pending items
   - /Plans - active plans
   - /Pending_Approval - items awaiting human review
   - /Done - completed items
2. Check /Logs for today's activity count
3. Update Dashboard.md with:
   - Current date/time
   - Folder counts
   - Recent activity summary
   - Today's focus items
4. Keep the format clean and readable

## Rules
- Update after every major action
- Keep the dashboard concise
- Always include the timestamp
- Never remove the existing structure
